            . On the 17th of this month, Mrs. Rail pulled the prisoner into my room, and locked her in. I saw her drop this shirt and cloke in my room; and I searched her, and took two caps from out of her bosom. (Produced and deposed to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I went up to enquire for one Mrs. Jones. I met the woman; she said, No Mrs. Jones lived there. I had these things under my arm. Then I said, it is a sad thing; for I had got a bundle that did not belong to Mrs. Jones.</p>
